    "original_url": "https://radiodalsan.com/2026/07/21/hindiya-oo-44-buruud-badeed-ku-xukuntay-dhammaan-nolosha/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=hindiya-oo-44-buruud-badeed-ku-xukuntay-dhammaan-nolosha",
    "country": "Somalia",
